            "CSAFPID-0005"
          ]
        },
        {
          "category": "mitigation",
          "details": "Use the IP filter function to restrict the connectable IP addresses. See MELSEC iQ-R Ethernet User's Manual (Application) 1.13 Security “IP filter” for more information.",
