        },
        {
          "category": "mitigation",
          "details": "If Port 5007 of the MELSOFT transmission port (TCP/IP) is not used, set b2 to \"1\" in advance. See MELSEC iQ-R Ethernet User's Manual (Application) Appendix 3, Buffer Memory for more information.",
